directions: ["Cut steak into thin strips.", "Sprinkle with meat tenderizer. Brown in oil in skillet.", "Cut green peppers into thin strips.", "Add onion, garlic, green peppers and celery to steak.", "Saute for about 2 minutes or until vegetables are partially tender.", "Combine cornstarch, beef stock and soy sauce; add to steak mixture.", "Cook, stirring, until liquid is slightly thickened and begins to simmer. Add salt and pepper.", "Serve immediately over rice."]
NER: ["beef stock", "salt", "green peppers", "salad oil", "soy sauce", "onion", "celery", "boneless chuck steak", "clove garlic", "cornstarch", "unseasoned meat tenderizer"]

title: Never Fail Icing
ingredients: ["1 stick margarine", "2 c. powdered sugar", "8 oz. cream cheese"]
directions: ["In a small bowl, beat margarine and cream cheese.", "Add sugar till desired thickness.", "Mix well."]

title: Sunny Banana Pie
ingredients: ["1 (9-inch) graham cracker crust", "2 bananas (very ripe)", "1 (8 oz.) pkg. cream cheese", "2 c. milk", "1 (3 1/4 oz.) pkg. instant vanilla pudding mix", "1/2 c. coconut (flaked)"]
directions: ["Slice bananas into crust. Gradually add 1/2 cup milk to softened cream cheese, mixing until well blended.", "Add pudding mix and rest of milk.", "Beat slowly 1 minute.", "Pour into crust and chill. Garnish with toasted coconut."]
NER: ["graham cracker crust", "instant vanilla pudding mix", "cream cheese", "bananas", "coconut", "milk"]

title: Strawberry Salad
ingredients: ["2 small pkg. strawberry jello", "1 c. boiling water", "2 small pkg. thawed strawberries", "3 bananas, mashed", "1 large can crushed pineapple", "1 c. chopped nuts", "1 pkg. sour cream"]
directions: ["Mix ingredients together.", "Pour 1/2 into mold and chill until firm.", "Spread with sour cream.", "Top with remaining jello and chill overnight."]

title: Cinnamon Sweet Pickles
ingredients: ["7 lb. cucumbers", "1 bottle red food coloring", "3 c. vinegar", "10 c. sugar", "1 gal. water", "1 c. lime", "2 Tbsp. alum", "2 c. water", "8 cinnamon sticks", "10 oz. bag red hots"]
directions: ["Peel and seed cucumbers (slice).", "Soak cucumbers in one cup of lime per gallon of water for 24 hours.", "Mix 1 cup of vinegar, red food coloring, alum and enough water to cover cucumbers.", "Simmer for 2 hours.", "Pour off."]
